geo.el NEWS -- history of user-visible changes.

Copyright (c) 2020 Would (oldosfan)
See the end of the file for license conditions.

This file is about changes in geo.el version 2.0.

* User-visible changes:

** Heading support in `geo-xdg'
The variable and hook `geo-xdg-last-heading' and
`geo-xdg-heading-changed-hooks' respectively provide support for
retrieving the current heading of the device.

** Heading support in `geo'
The hook and function `geo-heading-changed-hook' and
`geo-last-heading' respectively provide support for retrieving
the heading of the device.

